title: Nobuo Uematsu Collection Vol.1  Blue Dragon,FF,Hanjuku Hero etc
description:
A collection of Nobuo Uematsu albums and other rarities, the first batch includes:

~ Blue Dragon OST
~ Final Fantasy I & II (Origins) OST
~ Final Fantasy III OST (Nintendo DS)
~ Final Fantasy IX OST
~ Final Fantasy IX PLUS OST
~ Final Fantasy VII OST
~ Final Fantasy VII Advent Children OST (CGI Movie)
~ Final Fantasy VII to XI Lost Tracks (Rarities)
~ Final Fantasy VIII OST 
~ Final Fantasy VIII Fithos Lusec Wecos Vinosec (Orchestra album)
~ Hanjuku Hero VS 3D 

All ripped in very high quality MP3 (APX VBR)!!!
